kout database update' => '流体结账数据库更新','Some changes to the database are required. As with any update, we recommend you to <strong>take a full backup of your website before proceeding</strong>.' => '需要对数据库进行一些更改。与任何更新一样，我们建议您在进行更新之前<strong>对网站进行完整备份</strong>。','Update database' => '更新数据库','Fluid Checkout is not compatible with the Divi Builder checkout layout' => 'Fluid Checkout 与 Divi Builder 结账布局不兼容','<p>Fluid Checkout needs the classic WooCommerce shortcode-based checkout form to work. When using the Divi Builder to customize the look and feel of the checkout page, the classic shortcodes are replaced with custom widgets from the Divi Builder for each part of the checkout page. These custom widgets are not compatible with Fluid Checkout.</p><p>Please edit your checkout page replacing the Divi Builder widgets with the a text widget containing the shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code>.</p>' => '<p>Fluid Checkout 需要使用基于 WooCommerce 简码的经典结账表单。当使用 Divi 创建工具自定义结账页面的外观和感觉时，经典的快捷代码会被 Divi 创建工具中用于结账页面各部分的自定义部件所取代。这些自定义部件与 Fluid Checkout 不兼容。</p><p>请编辑您的结账页面，将 Divi 创建工具部件替换为包含简码 <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> 的文本部件。','Edit the checkout page' => '编辑结账页面','Read the documentation.' => '阅读文件。','Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature needs to be disabled when using Fluid Checkout' => '使用 Fluid Checkout 时，需要禁用德语化的 PRO 多步骤结账功能','When using Fluid Checkout, the multistep feature from the Germanized PRO plugin becomes unnecessary and can cause <strong>critical errors while processing new orders</strong>. Please disable the Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature in the plugin settings.' => '使用 Fluid Checkout 时，Germanized PRO 插件的多步骤功能变得不必要，并可能在处理新订单时导致 <strong>关键错误</strong>。请在插件设置中禁用 Germanized PRO 多步骤结账功能。','Go to Germanized settings' => '转到德语设置','Thanks for choosing Fluid Checkout!' => '感谢您选择 Fluid Checkout！','You have been using the plugin for a while now. How do you like it so far? <br>Please give us a quick rating, we appreciate every bit of feedback and it encourages us to keep improving the plugin :)' => '您使用该插件已有一段时间了。到目前为止，您觉得它怎么样？<br>请给我们一个快速评价，我们感谢每一点反馈，它鼓励我们不断改进插件:)','Rate the plugin' => '为插件评分','I need help!' => '我需要帮助！','Some features of WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers might not work as expected when using it with Fluid Checkout. Read <a href="%s">our documentation</a> for more information and alternative solutions.' => '与 Fluid Checkout 一起使用时，Quadlayers 的 WooCommerce Checkout Manager 的某些功能可能无法正常工作。请阅读<a href="%s">我们的文档</a>，了解更多信息和替代解决方案。','Read documentation' => '阅读文件','Don\'t show this again' => '不要再放这个了','Special offers' => '特别优惠','Extend all the goodness of Fluid Checkout to your cart page and thank you pages.' => '将 Fluid Checkout 的所有优点扩展到购物车页面和感谢页面。','Fluid Checkout PRO' => '流体检查仪 PRO','Design templates, optimized cart and order received pages, account matching, and much more.' => '设计模板、优化购物车和订单接收页面、账户匹配等等。','The best tools to further <strong>improve your WooCommerce checkout conversion rate</strong> and make the purchase experience consistent on the entire journey.' => '用于进一步<strong>提高 WooCommerce 结账转化率</strong>并使整个旅程的购买体验保持一致的最佳工具。','More design templates' => '更多设计模板','Optimized cart page' => '优化购物车页面','Optimized order received / thank you page' => '优化订单接收/感谢页面','Edit cart contents at checkout page' => '在结账页面编辑购物车内容','Account matching / user matching' => '账户匹配/用户匹配','Express Checkout buttons from supported payment methods' => '支持的付款方式中的快速结账按钮','Trust symbols on the cart and thank you pages' => '购物车和感谢页面上的信任符号','More positions for the coupon code on the checkout page' => '优惠券代码在结账页面的更多位置','Integrated coupon code field on the cart page' => '在购物车页面集成优惠券代码字段','International phone numbers' => '国际电话号码','Gift messages and packing slips' => '礼品信息和包装单','Local pickup and in-store collection' => '当地取货和店内取货','Upgrade to PRO &mdash; 99 EUR' => '升级至专业版 &mdash; 99 欧元','Fluid Checkout PRO – Bundle' => '流体结账专业版 - 捆包','All PRO features + All add-ons for a special price.' => '所有专业功能 + 所有附加组件，价格优惠。','The bundle includes all add-ons we currently offer and Fluid Checkout add-ons we launch in the future.' => '该捆绑包包括我们目前提供的所有附加组件和我们将来推出的 Fluid Checkout 附加组件。','226 EUR value (Save 42%)' => '价值 226 欧元（节省 42）','Google Address Autocomplete' => '谷歌地址自动完成','Address Book' => '地址簿','EU-VAT Assistant' => '欧盟增值税助理','All future add-ons *' => '所有未来附加组件 *','* For as long as you have an active subscription.' => '* 只要您还在使用订阅服务。','Get the Bundle – Only 129 EUR' => '获取套餐 - 仅 129 欧元','All prices shown in EUR. If there are any divergencies with the prices on our website, the offers shown on the website superseed these and will be applied.' => '所有价格均以欧元显示。如果与我们网站上的价格有任何差异，则以网站上的报价为准。','Add-ons' => '附加组件','Enhance your checkout experience with these add-ons.' => '使用这些附加组件增强您的结账体验。','I already have it – Hide this offer' => '我已经有了 - 隐藏此优惠','Installed &mdash; Activate' => '安装 &mdash; 激活','Activated' => '激活','Up to 40% less checkout fields to fill in.' => '最多可减少 40% 的结账填写字段。','Avoid delivery delays and unsatisfied customers. Collect the <strong>correct address information</strong> from the first time they buy with you.' => '避免送货延误和客户不满意。在客户第一次向您购买时，就收集<strong>正确的地址信息</strong>。','Get this add-on &mdash; 29 EUR' => '获取此附加组件 &mdash; 29 欧元','Address book' => '地址簿','Multiple saved addresses for shipping and billing.' => '为发货和账单保存多个地址。','Let customers <strong>save multiple shipping and billing addresses</strong> on their account and choose which ones to use at checkout and cart pages.' => '让客户<strong>在其账户中保存多个送货地址和账单地址</strong>，并在结账和购物车页面中选择使用哪个地址。','Get this add-on &mdash; 59 EUR' => '获取此附加组件 &mdash; 59 欧元','Simplified EU-VAT validation for your store.' => '为您的商店简化欧盟增值税验证。','Collect and <strong>validate EU VAT numbers at the checkout page</strong>, removes tax charges on reverse charge basis and confirms customer location when needed.' => '在结账页面收集和<strong>验证欧盟增值税号</strong>，根据反向收费原则移除税费，并在需要时确认客户所在地。','Get this add-on &mdash; 39 EUR' => '获取此附加组件 &mdash; 39 欧元','All add-ons are sold separately and require the <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite</strong> plugin to be installed and activated, except when noted.' => '所有附加组件均单独销售，并且需要安装和激活 <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite</strong> 插件，除非另有说明。','Select an image' => '选择图像','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to get your license key, or <a href="%s" target="_blank">purchase a new license key</a>.' => '<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">登录您的帐户</a>获取许可证密钥，或 <a href="%s" target="_blank">购买新的许可证密钥</a>。','Valid until %s.' => '有效期至 %s。','Expired on %s.' => '已于 %s 到期。','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to renew your license key and continue to receive updates and support.' => '<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">登录到您的账户</a>，更新许可证密钥并继续接收更新和支持。','License key cancelled.' => '许可证密钥已取消。','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Purchase a new license key</a> and continue to receive updates and support.' => '<a href="%s" target="_blank">购买新的许可证密钥</a>并继续接收更新和支持。','Error: ' => '错误：','Setup & Documentation' => '设置和文档','Great! Your checkout page is now running on Fluid Checkout.' => '太好了！您的结账页面现在已在 Fluid Checkout 上运行。','Here are a few resources for you to get started:' => '这里有一些资源供您开始使用：','Read the installation guide <a href="%s" target="_blank">Getting stated with Fluid Checkout</a>.' => '请阅读安装指南<a href="%s" target="_blank">使用流体检出</a>。','Setup layout and design on the <a href="%s">checkout options</a>.' => '在<a href="%s">结账选项</a>上设置布局和设计。','Check if there are any <a href="%s">integration options</a> available for other plugins you have installed.' => '检查您安装的其他插件是否有<a href="%s">集成选项</a>可用。','Visit <a href="%s" target="_blank">our documentation</a> for more information about Fluid Checkout features.' => '请访问 <a href="%s" target="_blank">我们的文档</a>，了解有关 Fluid Checkout 功能的更多信息。','If you ever need help, <a href="%s" target="_blank">open a support ticket</a> on our official support channel.' => '如果您需要帮助，<a href="%s" targe